# Benchmark results — never commit
# Numbers go stale every dep/version/hardware change; they're
# environment-specific; they shouldn't be cited as defensible KYA
# performance characteristics. The benchmark SCRIPT
# (examples/benchmark_kya_latency.py) ships in the repo so anyone
# can re-run; the measurement OUTPUTS stay local.
docs/BENCHMARKS.md
docs/FIDDLER_VS_KYA.md
benchmark_results/
*.benchmark.json
*.benchmark.csv

